    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors not assessed due to epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification planned but not yet executed. The assessment team concludes that sufficient evidence has been compiled to support submission and accepts the package for regulatory filing pending resolution of open items in the next assessment cycle.",
